init_text:
Are We Being Bad Citizens If We Don't Keep Up With the News?

In your opinion, are we being bad citizens if we don't keep up with the news? Do you think all people have some responsibility to know what is going on in the world? Does engaging with current events actually do anything at all? Why do you think the way you do?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In an ideal situation, we would all be actively contributing to the betterment of our countries and globe.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The reason I think this is because only when everyone is engaged, can we feel real positive change.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Only by participating can we find solutions and prevent problems.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When I think of the power behind people coming together, I think of this:

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When we want something, we have to speak up.
